title: Rare Studio Availability at 188 Octavia | August 27th
posting_body: ['Welcome to 188 Octavia', 'A boutique collection of 28 design-centric studios and two-bedroom apartments in the heart of Hayes Valley by DM Development.188 Octavia offers a thoughtfully-curated array of features, finishes and amenities for a fulfilling contemporary lifestyle in Hayes Valley.', ' Designed to maximize light and views from floor-to-ceiling windows, the stylish studio and two-bedroom homes combine rigorous contemporary design with high-quality finishes for an inspired urban lifestyle.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Interactive Touch Screen & Bluetooth Intercom', 'White Quartz Composite Countertops', '2N IP Verso Lobby Entry System', 'Lanz Modern Cabinets', 'Double-Tiered Bike Parking System', 'InSinkErator Badger 5XP Disposal', 'Silent Operation Dishwasher', 'Community Roof Deck', 'Cast-Concrete Outdoor Kitchen & BBQ', 'Zephyr Range Hood', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Roller Shades', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Check out the virtual tour: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
